msgid "Learn more about our mission, values, and the team behind our success"
msgstr "Soma byinshi ku ntego zacu, indangagaciro zacu n'ikipe ituma dutsinda"

msgid "Our Story"
msgstr "Amateka yacu"

msgid "Founded in 2015, Bika began with a simple mission: to provide businesses with powerful, accessible solutions that drive growth and efficiency. What started as a small team of passionate developers has grown into a comprehensive business solutions provider serving clients across multiple industries."
msgstr "Yashinzwe mu 2015, Bika yatangiye ifite intego yoroshye: guha ubucuruzi ibisubizo bikomeye kandi bigezweho bituma bwaguka kandi bukorana neza. Icyatangiye ari ikipe nto y'abashakashatsi bafite ishyaka cyakuze kiba ikigo gitanga ibisubizo byuzuye by'ubucuruzi gikorera abakiriya mu nzego zitandukanye."

msgid "In 2026, we are proud to be leading the digital transformation in Rwanda and beyond. Our commitment to innovation and customer success has been the driving force behind everything we do."
msgstr "Mu 2026, twishimiye kuba tuyoboye impinduka mu by'ikoranabuhanga mu Rwanda no hanze yarwo. Kwiyemeza kwacu guhanga udushya no gutsinda kw'abakiriya nibyo bituyobora muri byose dukora."

