msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Intego yacu"

msgid "To empower businesses of all sizes with innovative, accessible technology solutions that drive efficiency, growth, and competitive advantage in an ever-evolving digital landscape."
msgstr "Guha ubushobozi ubucuruzi bw'ingeri zose hifashishijwe ibisubizo by'ikoranabuhanga bishya kandi bigezweho bituma bukorana neza, bwaguka, kandi bukagira inyungu mu muvuduko w'ikoranabuhanga."

msgid "Our Vision"
msgstr "Icyerekezo cyacu"

msgid "To become the leading provider of business transformation solutions, recognized for our commitment to excellence, innovation, and creating lasting value for our clients and communities."
msgstr "Kuba ikigo kiyoboye mu gutanga ibisubizo by'impinduka mu bucuruzi, kizwiho gukora neza, guhanga udushya, no guha agaciro karambye abakiriya bacu n'abaturage."

