msgid "How does real-time inventory tracking work?"
msgstr "Ni gute gukurikirana ibicuruzwa mu buryo bw'ako kanya bikora?"

msgid "Our real-time inventory tracking uses barcode scanning, RFID technology, and API integrations to provide instant updates on stock levels. Every movement - from receiving to sales - is tracked automatically, giving you up-to-the-minute accuracy across all locations."
msgstr "Gukurikirana ibicuruzwa byacu mu buryo bw'ako kanya bikoresha gusikana barcode, ikoranabuhanga rya RFID, no guhuza na API kugira ngo bitange amakuru y'ako kanya ku ngano y'ibicuruzwa bihari. Buri kintu cyose - kuva kwakira kugeza kugurisha - gukurikiranwa mu buryo bwikora, bikaguha ukuri kw'ako kanya mu bice byose."

msgid "Can Bika handle multiple warehouse locations?"
msgstr "Ese Bika ishobora gucunga ububiko bwinshi mu bice bitandukanye?"

msgid "Yes! Bika supports unlimited warehouse locations with centralized management. You can track inventory across multiple sites, transfer stock between locations, and set location-specific reorder points and pricing."
msgstr "Yego! Bika ishobora gucunga ububiko butagira imipaka bufite imicungire ihuriye hamwe. Ushobora gukurikirana ibicuruzwa mu bice bitandukanye, kwimurira ibicuruzwa hagati y'ububiko, no gushyiraho igihe cyo kongera gutumiza n'ibiciro byihariye kuri buri hantu."

msgid "How accurate is the demand forecasting?"
msgstr "Ese isesengura ry'ibikenewe mu gihe kizaza ryizerwa ku rugero ruri he?"

msgid "Our AI-powered demand forecasting achieves 85-95% accuracy by analyzing historical sales data, seasonal trends, market conditions, and promotional activities. The system continuously learns and improves its predictions over time."
msgstr "Isesengura ryacu rikoresha ikoranabuhanga rya AI rigera ku rugero rwa 85-95% ruriho ukuri hifashishijwe isesengura ry'ibarurishamibare ry'ibyagurishijwe, ibihe, imiterere y'isoko, n'ibikorwa byo kwamamaza. Sisitemu igenda yiga kandi ikanoza ibyo ibona uko igihe gihita."

msgid "How long does implementation typically take?"
msgstr "Ubusanzwe gushyira sisitemu mu bikorwa bifata igihe kingana iki?"

msgid "Implementation time varies based on business size and complexity. Most businesses are up and running within 2-4 weeks. We provide a dedicated implementation specialist to ensure a smooth transition."
msgstr "Igihe cyo gushyira mu bikorwa giterwa n'ingano y'ubucuruzi n'imiterere yabwo. Ubucuruzi bwinshi butangira gukoresha sisitemu mu byumweru 2 kugeza kuri 4. Dutanga inzobere igufasha kugira ngo impinduka zigende neza."

msgid "Do you offer data migration services?"
msgstr "Ese mutanga serivisi zo kwimura amakuru?"

msgid "Yes, we provide comprehensive data migration services. Our team can help migrate your existing inventory data, customer information, and historical records from most common systems including Excel, QuickBooks, and other inventory management software."
msgstr "Yego, dutanga serivisi zishitse zo kwimura amakuru. Ikipe yacu ishobora kugufasha kwimura amakuru y'ibicuruzwa ufite ubu, amakuru y'abakiriya, n'ibarurishamibare rya kera bituruka muri sisitemu zikoreshwa cyane nk'Excel, QuickBooks, n'izindi sofutiweri zicunga ibicuruzwa."

msgid "What's included in the free trial?"
msgstr "Ni iki kiba kiri muri porogaramu y'igerageza y'ubuntu?"

msgid "Our 14-day free trial includes access to all core features: inventory tracking, basic reporting, up to 1000 SKUs, and standard integrations. You'll have full functionality to test the system with your business data."
msgstr "Igerageza ryacu ry'iminsi 14 ry'ubuntu ririmo kwinjira muri serivisi z'ingenzi zose: gukurikirana ibicuruzwa, raporo z'ibanze, kugeza ku bicuruzwa 1000, no guhuza na sisitemu zisanzwe. Uzaba ufite ubushobozi bwose bwo kugerageza sisitemu ukoresheje amakuru y'ubucuruzi bwawe."

msgid "Are there any hidden fees?"
msgstr "Ese hari amafaranga yaba yihishe umuntu atazi?"

msgid "No hidden fees. Our pricing is transparent and includes all standard features. Additional costs may apply for premium integrations, custom development, or dedicated support services, which are always discussed upfront."
msgstr "Nta madorari yihishe ahari. Ibiciro byacu birasobanutse kandi bikubiyemo serivisi zose zisanzwe. Hashobora kwiyongeraho ikiguzi ku bintu byihariye, gukora sisitemu yihariye, cyangwa ubufasha bwihariye, ariko ibyo bibanza kuganirwaho."

msgid "Which e-commerce platforms do you integrate with?"
msgstr "Ni izihe mbuga zicuruza kuri murandasi muhuza na zo?"

msgid "We integrate with all major e-commerce platforms including Shopify, WooCommerce, Magento, BigCommerce, and Amazon. Custom integrations are also available for proprietary systems."
msgstr "Duhuza n'imbuga zose zikomeye zicuruza kuri murandasi zirimo Shopify, WooCommerce, Magento, BigCommerce, na Amazon. Ushobora no guhuzwa n'izindi sisitemu zihariye."

msgid "Still Have Questions?"
msgstr "Ese uracyfite ibibazo?"

msgid "Our support team is here to help you get the answers you need."
msgstr "Ikipe yacu ishinzwe ubufasha iri hano kugira ngo iguhe ibisubizo ukeneye."

